Janiva Ellis (amụrụ n'afọ 1987) bụ ónyé America na-ese ihe nke bi na Brooklyn, NY na Los Angeles, CA. Ellis na-emekarị ihe osise ihe atụ nké na-enyocha ahụmịhe ụmụ nwanyị Africa-America.

A mụrụ ya na Oakland, California, Ellis kwagara Hawaii mgbè ọ dị afọ 7, na-agagharị n'etiti agwaetiti Kauai na Oahu. N'ịbụ ónyé nne ya na-acha ọcha zụlitere, na steeti nwere obéré ndị isi ojii, Ellis na-eji ọrụ nka ya nyochaa ma nyochaa mgbagwoju anya agbụrụ dị mgbagwoju ike nke ịzụlite ya. Ellis gụrụ ihe osise na California College of the Arts na San Francisco, gụsịrị akwụkwọ na 2012.

Ellis na-akọwa ihe osise ya dị ka ọ bụghị naanị mgbalị ịgwa ụmụ nwanyị na-abụghị ndị isi ojii ahụmahụ m, kamakwa ịkpọ ụmụ nwanyị ojii ndị ọzọ, ị na-eche nke a, kwa? Ndị nkatọ etoola Ellis maka nrụgide psychoanalytic na ihe osise ya. Mgbe ụfọdụ, ihe osise ahụ na-etinye ihe nnọchianya okpukpe; dị ka ụmụ atụrụ ma ọ bụ ndị mmụọ ozi, na-ezo aka na Canon nke ihe osise okpukpe. N'afọ 2017, Ellis gosipụtara "Lick Shot" na 47 Canal, ihe ngosi mbụ ya na New York City. N'afọ 2018, Ellis sonyere na New Museum Triennial - ːSongs for Sabotage. A gụnyere Ellis na 2019 Whitney Biennial nkè Rujeko Hockley na Jane Panetta haziri.
